CustomField.description: This is the date and time at which we first attempted to contact this lead. If blank, we have not attempted to contact them. The date is auto-populated via a flow when criteria are met that determine we can set this value - as specified in that flow.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The time we first attempted to contact this lead. If blank, we have yet to attempt contact (or this lead was processed before we started capturing this information).
CustomField.label: Time of first contact attempt
